      "title": "20,000 MT of Urea for Tea Cultivations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Plantation Industries has decided to distribute 20,000 MT of urea fertilizer for tea cultivation.",
        "The fertilizer will be distributed through the Tea Small Holdings Development Authority.",
        "The Chairman of Tea Small Holdings Development Authority Thushara Priyadarshana noted that urea fertilizer will be distributed through small tea estate societies and tea factories.a",
        "The Chairman also said that steps will be taken to provide the relevant fertilizer to farmers for a reasonable price.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe sworn in as 8th Executive President of Sri Lanka",
        "\u2018I am a friend of the people, but forced occupation of offices is illegal\u2019 \u2013 President"
